Mercantile Secures $73 Million Small-Business Funds From World Bank’s IFC

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-06-30T13:51:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-30/mercantile-secures-73-million-small-business-funds-from-world-bank-s-ifc.html
The World Bank’s International
Finance Corp. said it has arranged 50 million euros of funding
for  South Africa ’s  Mercantile Bank Holdings Ltd. (MTL)  to increase
lending to small businesses, particularly in the renewable
 energy industry  and in projects aiming to reduce carbon dioxide
emissions.  The IFC commented in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  